<template>
  <n-result
    status="500"
    title="500 服务器娘炸毛了"
    description="你可能需要更关心一点自己的员工"
  >
    <template #footer>
      <n-dropdown @select="handleSelect" trigger="hover" :options="options">
      <n-button type="primary" @click="handleClick"
        >点击散财消灾。没钱？那还是听歌吧</n-button
      >
      </n-dropdown>
    </template>
  </n-result>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    function handleClick() {
      window.open("https://res.kcn3388.club/music.html", "_blank");
    }
    return {
      handleClick,
    };
  },
});
</script>
